    }

    void baz(int i, int j) {
    }
}

EB:
When accepting the code completion suggestion, only the code after x.foo() should be replaced, not the entire line. The code is changed to:

baz(x.foo().foo())

I would rather it gave me:

baz(x.foo()x.foo())

